name: Empty Cartridge
description:
Empty catridge

You got bored of your job and used the printer to show others of your abilities, by bathing them in ink! 

But the printer keeps claiming that the cyan ink is missing!!!

Controls

(PC/PS/Xbox)

WASD/Left joystick: movement

Shift/L1/LB : Dash

Left Click/A/X : Melee attack

Right Click/R1/RB : Range attack
